lead_paragraph: Breanna Stewart scored 19 points to lead top-ranked UConn to an 83-40 rout of Memphis on Saturday, extending the team's winning streak to 57 games and giving the Huskies their 23rd straight 20-win season.

headline.print_headline: UConn Routs Memphis 83-40 for 57th Consecutive Win
